ingredients: UNBLEACHED ENRICHED FLOUR (WHEAT FLOUR, MALTED BARLEY FLOUR, NIACIN, REDUCED IRON, THIAMIN MONONITRATE, RIBOFLAVIN, FOLIC ACID), WATER, VEGETABLE OIL (PALM OIL AND SOYBEAN OIL), CONTAINS 2% OR LESS OF EACH OF THE FOLLOWING: SALT, CALCIUM SULFATE, WHEAT FLOUR, DEXTROSE, SODIUM ACID PYROPHOSPHATE, SODIUM BICARBONATE, FUMARIC ACID, HYDROGENATED PALM OIL, MONOGLYCERIDES, MONOCALCIUM PHOSPHATE, CELLULOSE GUM, MALTODEXTRIN, CARRAGEENAN, SODIUM METABISULFITE, ENZYMES, CALCIUM PROPIONATE AND POTASSIUM SORBATE (TO RETARD SPOILAGE).
